I actually think embedding a “Cherenkov core” inside Kurage is stronger as an operational mechanism than as another daemon.

Kurage already answers “What does the medium look like?”

Cherenkov answers “Where is something moving through the medium faster than the medium can absorb?”

Those are complementary.

